	    Imaginary part of sinusoid, 
	    <m:math>
	      <m:apply>
		<m:imaginary/>
		<m:apply>
		  <m:exp/>
		  <m:apply>
		    <m:times/>
		    <m:imaginaryi/>
		    <m:apply>
		      <m:divide/>
		      <m:apply>
